<div class="hero-unit">
  <h1>Mixtape Sequencer</h1>
  <p>Ever wanted to see your playlist in order from start to finish? Want an interface to drag and drop the sequence of songs and share it with others? Want people to give you their opinions on what should be coming up?</p>
  <p>
      <% if current_user.nil? %>
      <%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-large' %> or 
      <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-large' %> today!
      <% end %>
  </p>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>No need to upload songs!</h2>
    <p>Songs can be found on YouTube or Soundcloud, so everyone will have access to the tunes you choose.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Feedback galore!</h2>
    <p>People can comment on your current playlist order to give you suggestions/opinions/tips/advice.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Public or private!</h2>
    <p>You can choose whether or not you want your Mixtape Sequence open for everyone, or for only your close friends.</p>
  </div>
</div>